        "value": "C-21591"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"dap_body\">​There is no value of&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"c\"><math alttext=\"c\"><semantics><mi>c</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>&nbsp;for which&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"f\"><math alttext=\"f\"><semantics><mi>f</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>&nbsp;is an even function.​</p>",
